		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><img src="http://i.imgur.com/nDf1MiP.jpg" alt="Image" /><br /><br />Looking closer at some of these layouts...it appears that Zelda, at one point at least, kept score and had a timer? Also some sort of 10-item grid at the top of the screen?<br /><br />Top-right map had some interesting stuff...looks like there were thoughts of a dragon or other creature that slid in and out of a block, similar to a Piranha Plant? Kinda wonder what the Japanese on that map means.

		

